title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Boeing 307 Stratoliner - Where to find the manual
description:
In this video we will have a quick look on where to find the manual for the Boeing 307 Stratoliner. Currently the manual is not available yet on the MSFS website but for those who already bought the aircraft there is good news because you already have it.

In the document below you will find where to locate the folder assuming you didn't move the packages to a different folder or drive:

https://flightsimulator.zendesk.com/hc/en-us/articles/7058492594588-How-to-install-mods-in-Microsoft-Flight-Simulator
